data.description: The tax assessors office noted this property as having "ABOVE AVERAGE CONSTRUCTION!" This impeccable 4 sided brick ranch on a FULL FINISHED BASEMENT, is situated on .58 of an acre, inside of 285 off of Cascade Rd./Veltre. Lavish updates have been made to this home to expand the square footage which include an open sunroom with sky lights, a laundry room, an oversized deck and a two car attached garage with automatic doors. The interior features plenty  windows, original well kept hardwood floors and granite countertops in kitchen. The basement holds a large sized bedroom, bathroom, built-in bar, plus plenty of additional room for entertaining and storage. This lovely home also has an irrigation system to ensure the lawn stays beautifully landscaped year round. Built in 1971, updated, lived in and being sold by its original owner makes this a MASTERPIECE as it is, and with a few updates this home will make for EXQUISITE CITY LIVING!AS-IS, NO DISCLOSURES will be provided.
